data.description: Sellers require closing by 5/30/24 with a rent back to 6/15/24. This home is absolutely stunning with lots of upgrades and an amazing backyard with custom landscaping with probably the best and most beautiful view of the lake. You are located in the hot neighborhood of Spence Crossing at the end of a quiet street with beautiful views of nature in the heart of Virginia Beach. This home is in beautiful condition for its seven-year age. Open Concept, 3 bedrooms, 2.1 baths detached condo with 2 car garage. Enjoy all the Spence Crossing amenities: Clubhouse, Pools, Playground, Basketball Courts, Walking Trails, and Green Space. Ground Maintenance, Water, Trash and Sewer are included in the monthly condo fees of $302 and POA/HOA $49 per month.
